# Comp Runner

A simple vim plugin for fast compilation and execution of competition solutions

## Installation

Choose your preferred method of installation

1. Pathogen : Clone repository in your bundle directory and restart vim.
```sh
$ git clone git@github.com:dhruvasagar/vim-comp.git ~/.vim/bundle
```
2. Vundle: Add this to your vimrc - `Plugin dhruvasagar/vim-comp`
3. NeoBundle : Add this to your vimrc - `NeoBundle dhruvasagar/vim-comp`

## Getting Started

Write program and hit <kbd>c\<CR></kbd> to compile and run it using vimux.
This works well when paired with `https://github.com/dhruvasagar/dotfiles/blob/master/bin/comp`

